parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the oil pressure sensor can cause the engine to malfunction, leading to oil leaks, engine damage, and potentially even engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Oil pressure warning light comes on
oil leaks from the engine
engine stalls or loses power
white smoke from the engine
engine oil light goes off and on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive engine sludge buildup can cause engine damage, leading to engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Large plumes of white smoke from the engine
engine stalls or loses power
engine warning lights illuminate
engine oil light goes off and on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded, especially if it occurs while driving at high speeds.
symptoms: Engine stalls without warning
loss of power
engine warning lights illuminate
check engine light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the timing chain tensioner can cause engine damage, leading to engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Timing chain slap or rattling noise
engine warning lights illuminate

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sliding door latch can cause the door to open unexpectedly while driving, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities. It can also cause inconvenience and discomfort for passengers.
symptoms: The sliding door does not latch shut
the door opens unexpectedly while driving
the door opens with excessive force
the door is difficult to open or close manually
the door latch fails to engage
the door opens while turning or making a left turn
the door opens at varying speeds
the door opens while stationary.

the rear hatch door opens intermittently

the rear hatch door fails to open after sitting in the sun for an extended period.
